Reasoning: The problem of managing QoE for video streaming for mobile clients is a common problem in the field of computer networks and communication systems, which falls under the sub-category of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of approximation algorithms and the analysis of the complexity of the problem suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AL (Algorithms and Complexity). The use of linear functions and the analysis of the problem as an instance of the Santa Clause Problem suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
